                <salute>Dear Herbert</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I have rec'd your letter. Nothing now remains but a sweet &#38; rich
                memory&#8212;none more beautiful, all time, all life, all the earth&#8212;</p><p>&#8212;I cannot
                write any thing of a letter to-day. I must sit alone &#38; think.<ptr
                    target="upa.00081_n2"/></p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
